record.title: NATIONAL NURSES WEEK

speaking.paragraph: Madam President, I ask unanimous consent that the HELP Committee be discharged from further consideration of S. Res. 192.

record.chair: Without objection, it is so ordered. The clerk will report the resolution by title.
record.narrative: The legislative clerk read as follows:

speaking.paragraph: I ask unanimous consent that the resolution be agreed to, the preamble be agreed to, the motion to reconsider be laid on the table, and any statements relating thereto be printed in the Record.

record.chair: Without objection, it is so ordered.
